  "texts": [
    "Following Institutional Review Board approval, unit leaders in treatment and control groups, were instructed via an operations order to share with their service member an easy-to-remember URL for the secure, online survey, as well as an overview and FAQ about the study; unit leaders did not know whether service members participated.",
    "All participants provided informed consent prior to data collection.",
    "Our goal was 1580 completed surveys at baseline based on our power analyses.",
    "A total of 2216 surveys were completed at baseline (i.e., 70% or more of questions answered); after excluding service members who were members of battalions that were not part of the study and those who self-identified as platoon leaders, therefore would be potentially targeted for the intervention, the sample of eligible service members was 1890, approximately 37.8% of the estimated sample population.",
    "The allocation to intervention and survey-only control groups was evenly split with NI=948 (50.2%) and Nc = 942 (49.8%)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}